<br />

<br />
2)  What stats are important to a Bard, based on what type of styles?
<br />

<br />
3)  What is &quot;fade&quot;, and why does INT have anything to do with it?
<br />

<br />
4)  How/when does a Bard use mana? (&lt;-----???????)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Thank you, drive through!
<br />

